Title: 091: Lessons From a Successful Career in Data Visualization
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the Head Coach at The Information Lab, Andy Kriebel. You will learn how to maintain a Data Viz Blog, how to be a Tableau Zen Master and hear about how discovering Tableau at Coca-Cola changed Andy's career trajectory.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/91
